  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688890/extras/9f20cde06c4d56d5437c3a66b5d087f2.poster.avif?t=1706188124\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688890/extras/9f20cde06c4d56d5437c3a66b5d087f2.webm?t=1706188124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688890/extras/9f20cde06c4d56d5437c3a66b5d087f2.mp4?t=1706188124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>A point and click puzzle adventure game set across multiple time periods. Discover and enjoy this strange and surreal story about a mysterious letter, a missing professor and a confusing mansion. With more than a hundred items, locations and objects to investigate, can you solve the mystery?</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688890/extras/43540250aa2ff793191120c430f1bea1.poster.avif?t=1706188124\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688890/extras/43540250aa2ff793191120c430f1bea1.webm?t=1706188124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688890/extras/43540250aa2ff793191120c430f1bea1.mp4?t=1706188124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Enjoy this classic adventure style game with mind bending puzzles. <br></li><li>Experience dry humour and a unique hand/mouse drawn art style.<br></li><li>Explore 40 locations across three time periods.<br></li><li>Find and investigate more than 100 unique items.<br></li><li>Endure brief mini games.<br></li><li>Discover multiple endings based on your actions.</li></ul><br><sp